content.headline: Joby to Install First Electric Air Taxi Charger in Greater New York City Region
content.summary: SANTA CRUZ, Calif., January 23, 2024--Joby Aviation, Inc. (NYSE:JOBY), a company developing electric vertical take-off and landing (eVTOL) aircraft for commercial passenger service, today announced it has signed a definitive agreement with Helo Holdings, Inc. ("HHI"), to install the first air taxi charger in the greater New York City region at the company’s heliport in Kearny, New Jersey, located just a two minute flight from Manhattan.
